ALTER VIEW univmed.dim_quadrante_medico
AS
SELECT
[KEY_CRM]
,[MERCADO_UNIV]
,[CATEGORIA_UNIV]
,[QUADRANTE_UNIV]
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://gsksynapseaccount.dfs.core.windows.net/gskoutputfiles/Universo Medico/dimensao_quadrante_medico_p_*.parquet',
        FORMAT='PARQUET'
    ) WITH (
[KEY_CRM]           VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[MERCADO_UNIV]		 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[CATEGORIA_UNIV]	 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8
,[QUADRANTE_UNIV]	 VARCHAR(50) COLLATE Latin1_General_100_BIN2_UTF8  
    ) as ROW
